nodes.text: Hi Person1, Yes I noted that and discussed it with Dr. Person2. He just got back to me this morning and advised me that we will just repeat scans in MM/DD/YYYY. I will place an order for them now if you would please give our office a call to get them scheduled. Generally one rise in PSA is not enough to say somethin g is wrong, it's just something that makes us keep a close eye on it. Thanks, Person3, LOCATION
